Providers of services and solutions for the assessment of claims and maintenance are dedicated to collecting information provided by manufacturers, then treating and offering them to their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex, of the North American Solara group, is the leading company; 80% of the estimates are made with its products.
Other companies competing in the field of sector assessment and information development tools are GtMotive and Eurotax.
The work with the data provided by the manufacturers is far from simple.
According to Eduardo Velázquez, commercial director of Audatex, the company in Spain with 63 manufacturers and importers, and each of them provides information in a different format.
In addition, the amount of data to be processed continues to increase, so that in the last five years more versions, variants and motorizations have been launched than in the previous fifteen years.
